    "key": "This character has consumed a substance, now in their bloodstream, that emits a kinetic field. This field gets stronger as their health deteriorates, eventually emitting a blue shimmer and producing a noticable effect on any blows that they deal, or that ",
    "original": "This character has consumed a substance, now in their bloodstream, that emits a kinetic field. This field gets stronger as their health deteriorates, eventually emitting a blue shimmer and producing a noticable effect on any blows that they deal, or that are dealt to them. They also claim to hear a constant, almost imperceptible whisper when alone, but that's probably superstition.",
    "translation": "这个角色摄入了一种物质，这种现在已经流淌在他血管的物质能产生一个动能场。这个场随着他们的健康状况恶化而变得更加强大，最终会产生蓝色波光，并对他们打出或受到的任何攻击产生显著影响。他还声称独自一人时总是听到几乎无法察觉也不曾断绝的耳语声，但这可能只是迷信。",
    "stage": 1,
    "context": "return \"This character has consumed a substance, now in their bloodstream, that emits a kinetic field. This field gets stronger as their health deteriorates, eventually emitting a blue shimmer and producing a noticable effect on any blows that they deal, or that are dealt to them. They also claim to hear a constant, almost imperceptible whisper when alone, but that's probably superstition.\";"
  },
